# Project Scope

- Mockup only — no backend, no auth, no HttpClient, no NgRx
- PrimeNG-first — check PrimeNG catalog before custom UI
- Section-based edits — change one section at a time; no cross-section refactors without ask
- No new npm packages without explicit approval
- All data from `src/app/data/` static files
- Nav items are visual placeholders — no routing
- **Dev verification:** user runs `pnpm start` — do not run or suggest `pnpm build` / `ng build` unless the user explicitly asks
